    <h1 class="page-header">About</h1>
    <p>
    This application, Platters, is a demonstration web application
    developed using the 
    <em><a href="http://rubyonrails.org" target="_blank">Ruby on Rails</a></em>
    web framework and associated technologies. Refer to 
    <%= link_to "details", details_path %> 
